title: How to Attract Success
itunes:title: How to Attract Success
description:
Episode 531 - The person that you are right now does not matter at all. It is not about who you are, it is about who you are becoming. That is why it is so important to make sure that you work every day at becoming a better version of yourself. In this episode, I talk about how to make it as easy as possible to become the person that you have always wanted to be.
